    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
        <td id="descriptionArea">
            机构代码：hwjxx<br/>
账号：15075496858<br/>
操作路径/课本位置：【数据-学习数据】全部任务-按老师15075496858<br/>
实际结果：有完成的任务，但是数据为0<br/>
预期结果：有完成的任务，数据不为0<br/>
其他说明：<br/>
<br/>
运营原话：<br/>
机构代码：hwjxx<br/>
老师账号：15075496858<br/>
时间：2026年2月<br/>
问题：老师在2月这期间是有布置任务的，且期间也有学员完成任务，但是后台数据老师这里数据都是0，帮忙看下怎么回事？
            <br/>
        </td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <br/>

    <table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" align="center">
    <tr>
        <td bgcolor="#bbbbbb" width="1%" nowrap align="center">
            &nbsp;<font color="#ffffff"><b>注释</b></font>&nbsp;
        </td>
        <td>&nbsp;</td>
    </tr>
    </table>

    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" class="grid" style="margin: 0;">
                <tr id="comment-header-382451"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            评论于 
                                                        <a class="user-hover" rel="zfwang" id="word_commented_zfwang" href="https://jira.51tyty.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zfwang">王之枫</a>
                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">12/&#19977;&#26376;/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-382451"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            SELECT<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`user_id` AS T_A30_3_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`nickname` AS T_A39_4_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`username` AS T_AE6_5_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;SUM(IFNULL(A83_T_2_.`com_task_count`, 0)) AS T_A17_6_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;SUM(IFNULL(A83_T_2_.`total_task_count`, 0)) AS T_A23_7_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;IFNULL(<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SUM(A83_T_2_.`com_task_count`) / SUM(A83_T_2_.`total_task_count`),<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;) AS T_AA7_8_,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;SUM(A83_T_2_.`score_sum`) / SUM(A83_T_2_.`com_hasscore_task_count`) AS T_A4E_9_<br/>
FROM<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;(<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;select<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`inst_id`,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`user_id`,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`username`,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;COALESCE(nickname_note, &#39;&#39;) = &#39;&#39;,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;nickname,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`nickname_note`<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;) as nickname,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;mobile<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;from<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`dcp_inst_user_info`<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;WHERE<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`inst_id` = &#39;252749&#39;<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and `role_id` != 6<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and `role_id` != 7<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;and `user_status` != 3<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;) AS A90_T_1_<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;LEFT JOIN (<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;select<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(total_task_count) as total_task_count,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(com_task_count) as com_task_count,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(total_signed_days) as total_signed_days,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(completed_signed_days) as completed_signed_days,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(score_sum) as score_sum,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sum(com_hasscore_task_count) as com_hasscore_task_count,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;count_date,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;teacher_id<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;FROM<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;dcp_teacher_task_count<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;WHERE<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`inst_id` = &#39;252749&#39;<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AND date_format(count_date, &#39;%Y-%m&#39;) = &#39;2026-02&#39;<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;group BY<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;teacher_id,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;count_date<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;) AS A83_T_2_ ON `A90_T_1_`.`user_id` = `A83_T_2_`.`teacher_id`<br/>
WHERE<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`mobile` LIKE &#39;%15075496858%&#39;<br/>
GROUP BY<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`user_id`,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`nickname`,<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;`A90_T_1_`.`username`<br/>
ORDER BY<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;T_AA7_8_ DESC<br/>
LIMIT<br/>
&nbsp;&nbsp;0, 20
        </td></tr>
                <tr id="comment-header-382465"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            评论于 
                                                        <a class="user-hover" rel="nxu" id="word_commented_nxu" href="https://jira.51tyty.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=nxu">徐宁</a>
                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">12/&#19977;&#26376;/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-382465"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            排查发现老师2月份没有布置任务，但是老师有个任务延续到了2月份
        </td></tr>
                <tr id="comment-header-382908"><td bgcolor="#f0f0f0">
            评论于 
                                                        <a class="user-hover" rel="jjxiao" id="word_commented_jjxiao" href="https://jira.51tyty.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=jjxiao">肖嘉俊</a>
                                        <font size="-2">
            [
                <font color="#336699">13/&#19977;&#26376;/26</font>

                            ]
            </font>

        </td></tr>
        <tr id="comment-body-382908"><td bgcolor="#ffffff">
            根据老师布置的任务开始时间来统计的，比如任务的日期是1.30~3.1日，那么学生在完成任务时，是算给在1.30日的
        </td></tr>
            </table>
肖嘉俊 通过JIRA 7.3.8#73019-sha1:94e8771b8094eef96c119ec22b8e8868d286fa88 生成于 Fri Mar 13 16:02:13 CST 2026。

